    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span id=\"page234R_mcid14\" class=\"markedContent\"><span dir=\"ltr\">Also, at 1st level, Hijutsu you cast that </span><span dir=\"ltr\">deals lightning damage to a creature currently under</span> <span dir=\"ltr\">the </span><span dir=\"ltr\">effects of the chilled condition takes +1 lightning </span><span dir=\"ltr\">damage for each rank of chilled that creature has.</span><br /><span dir=\"ltr\">Beginning at 11</span><span dir=\"ltr\">th</span> <span dir=\"ltr\">level, this bonus damage increases to </span><span dir=\"ltr\">+2. Beginning at 18</span><span dir=\"ltr\">th</span> <span dir=\"ltr\">level, this bonus damage increases </span><span dir=\"ltr\">to +3.</span></span></p>",
